results.title: Engraved Shell Pendant, Wood bead Necklace, Live Laugh Love, Sterling Silver Wire Wrapped, Gift For Her, Valentines Day, Handmade, Different
results.description:
"Live Laugh Love" who does not know this saying? You can find it engraved on T-Shirts, cups, wood and so on. ...Why not on a nice shell from the beach too?
With a small milling tool I  engraved that saying into this shell. Little hearts are added. The bail is made from 925 sterling silver wire. I added some cute sterling silver spirals to it to make it more interesting looking. It is attached to the bail with a long wire and with a special adhesive bonding compound. The wooden beads  are strung on a professional string . On the ends you can see nice wrapped o-rings and between them a handmade sterling silver s-hook clasp. The chain measures 29" total length, but you could hook the s-clasp wherever you like to change the length.
This is a nice long necklace to wear every day. 

It comes in a nice cardboard Jewelry box and ready to be given as a gift.
 
Please note: Shells are fragile and can break when dropped or hitting a hard surface.

If the sterling silver should tarnish over time, I advise you to clean it carefully with a liquid jewelry cleaner.

ABOUT OUR DECALS:

Our vinyl graphics are precision cut from high quality removable vinyl making it the perfect medium for decorating your home. You can install your favorite saying, scripture or quote on your application surface today and remove it when a new inspiration arises. Make your home uniquely personal with one of the latest trends in home décor! Vinyl decals give the elegant look of hand-painted lettering. All colors offered are a matte finish. Our decals are easy to apply and can be removed without damaging your application surface. Decals may come in several pieces to make application easier. You can also cut between images and place pieces however you choose!

You can order one of our patterns or we can create a custom work of art just for you. Great for family photo walls, custom frames, memory verses or just express yourself to friends and family.

PLEASE NOTE:

The listing photo is for display purposes only and may not depict the design to exact scale. Please see the measurements listed in the drop down menu and select the size you need. Please measure the space for your decal before purchasing to get an accurate representation of how the vinyl will look in your space.

APPLICATION INSTRUCTIONS: 

Installation instructions, please read all the instructions included with your order before starting and we advise watching the recommended YouTube video.

When you receive your decal, it is advisable to let your decal rest unfolded or unrolled on a flat surface for a few days before installing so that it can reach room temperature and flatten out from shipping for easier application. 

Our premium vinyl has a matte finish and is removable but is not reusable (i.e. can only be applied once to a surface) You can apply vinyl decals to most smooth surfaces like: smooth walls, metal, plastic, glass, mirror, appliances, floors, furniture, laptops, wood, marble, tile, etc…

Newly painted surfaces need at least a 20 day drying period. (Please be warned that if you do not wait for the allotted drying time with new paint, your decal may not adhere properly or may damage the paint during later removal of your decal.)

There are some surfaces that are not recommended for decal installation:
Rough textured surfaces, panel walls, or if you have VOC free paints (also known as green paints) or paint that contain Teflon. Extra low and especially zero VOC paints can be problematic... It is important to use your test decal on your chosen surface first to make sure that there are no installation problems or that it’s not sticking properly. We are not responsible for any damages that may occur during installation or removal of your wall decal.

This YouTube video helps in understanding the installation process.

results.title: Mental Health Unisex Sweatshirt
results.description:
I created this design after seeing one too many live laugh love signs. 
As someone who has struggled with mental health at times in my life and certainly this past year, I wanted to make something that spoke a little more truth but with a lightheartedness to it to help keep people smiling, when smiling is the last thing they think they can do. 
I give to you the survive- smirk- self love sweatshirt in green font ( the color of mental health awareness)
Survive because some days it's the bare minimum of what you can do and that's ok
Smirk because sometimes you can't smile, but a side smirk is just snarky enough to work 
Self love because that's where the healing starts, so when you're ready, do that
If you're gonna live in a sweatshirt, this is the one to do it in 
A sturdy and warm sweatshirt bound to keep you warm in the colder months. 
A pre-shrunk, classic fit sweater that's made with air-jet spun yarn for a soft feel and reduced pilling.

• 50% cotton, 50% polyester
• Pre-shrunk
• Classic fit with no center crease
• 1x1 athletic rib knit collar with spandex
• Air-jet spun yarn with a soft feel and reduced pilling
• Double-needle stitched collar, shoulders, armholes, cuffs, and hem
